      "comment": "HESITATE (4) broke gear when resuming behind multiple Group 1 winner Don Hugo in Sydney so prepared to forgive that result. He was a G3 winner last campaign and was runner-up in last year's Queensland Derby at this venue so he is a talent. Has won three of four second-up attempts so expect big improvement. JUNGLE DRAGON (10) may need some luck from the back row but looks suited back in trip and was an easy winner here three back. CREDULOUS (1) has been coming from wider or second row barriers but was a close second here the last time he had the ace draw. Can be competitive. FIRE RAISER (3) hasn't been far away since recording back-to-back wins, one of them here when off this barrier. Include.",
